data.description: Gorgeous single story home with highly sought after floor plan in Bay Colony Meadows subdivision. This house isn't missing a single detail.  Granite throughout and hardwood flooring. Open concept floor plan makes this house ideal for entertaining. Stunning high ceilings in the living room lead into the large master suite and designer master bath with his and her closets. Great size secondary bedrooms perfect for a growing family. Relax after a long day under the large covered patio with no back neighbors.  Backyard large enough to add a pool! This charming home wont last on the market long. Safe and quiet cul-de-sac street super close the the fwy, restaurants and grocery stores.
